  line `116. Order for custody an d disposal of property pending trial.`
  line `117. Order for disposal of property regarding which offence is committed.`
  line `118. Powers of Force Court in relation to proceedings under this Act.`
  line `119. Tender of pardon to accomplie s.`
  line `120. Trial of person not complying with conditions of pardon.`
